ndle Scribe can act as a notebook with an included stylus, which makes it a better gift for, say, students who like to take notes while researching for a paper — especially as it can convert handwriting into typed text.\n\nRead our reviews of the Kindle, Kindle Paperwhite, and Kindle Scribe.\n\n[Product: 2022 Amazon Kindle | https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BR67MQLG/?tag=theverge02-20, https://howl.me/cmb8nqhVnGI, https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Famazon-kindle-6-34-e-reader-black-2022-release%2F-%2FA-86976936&subid1=vergedealsbreakout050624]\n\n[Product: 2021 Kindle Paperwhite (with ads) | https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BDCCG44G?tag=theverge02-20, https://howl.me/cmb8xunzOF0, https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Famazon-kindle-paperwhite-6-8-34-16gb-e-reader-with-adjustable-warm-light-black%2F-%2FA-86976934&subid1=vergedealsbreakout050624]\n\n[Product: Kindle Scribe (16GB, Basic Pen)  | https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09BS26B8B?tag=theverge02-20, https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Famazon-kindle-scribe-10-2-34-16gb-e-reader-gray%2F-%2FA-88410166&subid1=vergedealsbreakout050624]\n"}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"http://schema.org/","@type":"ItemList","itemListOrder":"ItemListUnordered","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"item":{"@type":"Product","name":"2022 Amazon Kindle","image":"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24110035/226347_Kindle_SVasani_0004.jpg","description":"Amazon’s latest entry-level Kindle comes with a host of much-needed upgrades, including a better display, longer battery life, and USB-C charging.","url":"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BR67MQLG/","offers":[{"@type":"Offer","name":"2022 Amazon Kindle","price":99.99,"priceCurrency":"USD","url":"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BR67MQLG/","offeredBy":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Amazon"}},{"@type":"Offer","name":"2022 Amazon Kind